How to clone into the current working directory
c/o http://stackoverflow.com/a/16811212

# for read-only access
git init . && git remote add -t \* -f origin https://github.com/devietti/home.git && git checkout master

# for read-write access
git init . && git remote add -t \* -f origin git@github.com:devietti/home.git && git checkout master
